WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.400 --> 00:00:02.267
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:02.267 --> 00:00:03.543
Praise the Lord.

00:00:03.543 --> 00:00:05.600
Thank you for joining me today.

00:00:05.600 --> 00:00:06.960
Well, glory to God.

00:00:07.300 --> 00:00:13.740
I wasn't going to do a video today, but there's things on my heart that I would like to talk about.

00:00:13.740 --> 00:00:16.060
Diana is behind the camera.

00:00:16.060 --> 00:00:16.640
Hi.

00:00:16.640 --> 00:00:29.650
And she said, "Honey, after you did that video last night and the anointing was so strong in the house and we were interceding," she says, "it's been on my heart all day long.

00:00:29.650 --> 00:00:48.480
" You know, she's Apache and about the Trail of Tears and all of it, you know, about her ancestors and the Trail of Tears and the Native Americans and the suffering that they went through, you know, and all the different things, the hardship of people.

00:00:54.480 --> 00:01:05.270
But she said, "I feel in my spirit there's something more to what you saw about the African-American population last night, Brandon, and I don't know what it is, but I'm going to start searching.

00:01:05.270 --> 00:01:09.760
I want to study because I feel the spirit of the Lord has told me there's more.

00:01:09.760 --> 00:01:20.062
" And so, she was sitting on the couch and she started just, you know, my wife's very intelligent and she's over there tapping away and she goes, "Oh, I found it.

00:01:20.062 --> 00:01:23.733
" She came to me and she was crying, and she said, "Brandon, I found it.

00:01:23.733 --> 00:01:28.823
" She said, "Everything the Lord," she goes, "the Lord is so strategic in timing.

00:01:28.823 --> 00:01:30.970
" She goes, "Brandon, we live in Tulsa.

00:01:30.970 --> 00:01:43.025
" And she said, "I just found the Tulsa race riots started on May 31st of 1921, and they went until June 1st.

00:01:43.025 --> 00:01:50.384
" And she said 30 blocks of homes were burned from African-American men and women, businesses, everything.

00:01:50.384 --> 00:01:52.530
And they called it Black Wall Street.

00:01:52.530 --> 00:01:59.040
It was a wealthier part of one of the wealthiest black suburbs in America at the time.

00:01:59.040 --> 00:02:02.719
And there were 800 people that were hurt.

00:02:02.719 --> 00:02:07.566
Several—I think it was like 30, 40 people—lost their lives.

00:02:07.566 --> 00:02:12.040
36 total: 26 African-Americans and 10 white.

00:02:12.040 --> 00:02:12.834
Yep.

00:02:12.834 --> 00:02:17.599
A very tragic thing.

00:02:17.599 --> 00:02:30.560
And I just, wow, what was on, you know, when I come, you know, I let you in on something that's so private to Diana and me, our prayer time.

00:02:30.560 --> 00:02:42.300
You don't allow—it's very, for me, it's taken a learning curve for me to let people in because this is my walk that I've had since I've been 16.

00:02:42.300 --> 00:02:44.984
It's something I've developed.

00:02:44.984 --> 00:02:56.304
And when you sit at the Father's feet, He shows you what's on His heart.

00:02:56.304 --> 00:02:58.720
He shows you what's on His heart.

00:02:58.720 --> 00:03:04.617
He shows you what He's compassionate about—things that you think have been forgotten.

00:03:04.617 --> 00:03:17.199
Things like—I saw whenever I was in the spirit, I saw a rug, a big-looking rug, a throw rug, and it was being lifted up and it was used like a dustpan, and people wanted to brush all the dirt underneath it.

00:03:18.524 --> 00:03:26.263
And He said, "I'm going to take that rug up and I'm exposing the darkness, and I'm exposing the dirt underneath that rug.

00:03:26.263 --> 00:03:31.614
" Brandon, the hurt, the pain is real and it still exists in a lot of people.

00:03:31.614 --> 00:03:33.864
And I'm ready to heal it.

00:03:33.864 --> 00:03:36.400
I'm ready to set these people free.

00:03:36.400 --> 00:04:01.143
But not only that, I saw Harriet Tubman, the African-American woman with the purple durag, and it was amazing, folks, is that I saw pictures of her—my son Googled her and we started looking—with purple durags just like I saw, with the white shirt, when she was doing the Underground Railroad.

00:04:01.143 --> 00:04:03.759
But they called it Black Wall Street.

00:04:03.759 --> 00:04:11.147
And if you remember last night, I kept seeing Wall Street, Wall Street, and I saw New York City.

00:04:11.147 --> 00:04:23.813
And that was how the Lord was describing to me—not about New York City, it was a type and shadow of something that He was, because I'm seeing New York being painted in front of my face.

00:04:23.813 --> 00:04:27.783
But He doesn't tell me "Tulsa Wall Street" because I wouldn't have understood.

00:04:28.606 --> 00:04:40.800
He was talking to me directly about Wall Street in New York, and it was a type and shadow of what was going on with the race riots in Tulsa, Oklahoma.

00:04:40.800 --> 00:05:08.626
And my mind was—I'm humbled that He would want to take a bald-headed white guy, come on YouTube, and want me to pray for something so precious to Him.

00:05:19.670 --> 00:05:54.189
I don't know why me, all these people.

00:05:54.199 --> 00:06:07.935
God, what He allowed me to see last night, none of you can understand it.

00:06:07.935 --> 00:06:16.000
Even the African-American people that are here right now have a glimpse of what you've heard.

00:06:16.000 --> 00:06:33.120
But I went into the depth of the heart of it in the spirit, and I could feel it in intercession.

00:06:33.120 --> 00:06:47.430
Those people in chains and the pain they felt, so much God would give me glimpses of their heart.

00:06:47.440 --> 00:06:58.835
And words can't explain to you the bondage and the hopelessness that they felt, similar to, I'm sure, what the children of Israel felt for 400 years.

00:06:58.835 --> 00:07:05.519
But people, you can read a story, you can read a novel, you can read history books.

00:07:05.519 --> 00:07:07.062
That's what I'm trying to say.

00:07:07.062 --> 00:07:20.020
You can read history books, and you can hear about this woman with the purple rag, and we all think she's great, or Rosa Parks sitting in the back of the bus.

00:07:20.020 --> 00:07:30.960
These people, we hear about them, and maybe somebody might have known them, but a story is nothing until you feel it.

00:07:30.960 --> 00:07:34.000
That's what I'm trying to tell you.

00:07:34.000 --> 00:07:37.679
The Trail of Tears, I was there in the spirit realm.

00:07:37.679 --> 00:07:39.280
I could see the children.

00:07:39.280 --> 00:07:41.909
I could see these people walking in the snow.

00:07:41.909 --> 00:07:51.582
I could see they were barefoot and their feet were blistering with frostbite walking across the land.

00:07:51.582 --> 00:08:07.337
And I could see them, and they were so—they were tied up and they were going across the land, getting taken out of their area where they lived to be taken to Oklahoma, to these places, forced to leave, forced to do these things.

00:08:08.274 --> 00:08:14.015
It's pain beyond anybody's comprehension, if it was mine.

00:08:14.015 --> 00:08:17.759
And I'm not going to say here, "Well, I can relate, I can do all this.

00:08:17.759 --> 00:08:18.046
" No, no, no.

00:08:18.619 --> 00:08:19.984
I saw a glimpse.

00:08:19.984 --> 00:08:26.171
It's like opening up a book and you see it, and you open it up, you get a glimpse of something.

00:08:26.171 --> 00:08:28.065
But it's that way in the spirit.

00:08:28.065 --> 00:08:31.884
I got a glimpse of something, something that was very hurtful.

00:08:31.884 --> 00:08:46.240
And me as a white guy, I, like I said, I don't know why He chose me, but I am humbled, and I know what the Lord said.

00:08:46.240 --> 00:08:51.965
He said, "I've not forgotten your prayers," and I've heard that echo inside of my spirit.

00:08:51.965 --> 00:09:05.760
And I could see the prayers coming up from those African slaves in those camps with these wood huts, and they had little fires, and they were looking at the stars and they were looking at the North.

00:09:05.760 --> 00:09:09.400
And it was interesting because that Tubman lady, it was about the North Star.

00:09:09.400 --> 00:09:10.731
I could see the North Star.

00:09:23.310 --> 00:09:23.500
I could see the Big Dipper.

00:09:27.982 --> 00:09:31.232
I could see they were navigating by stars at night to get through because they didn't travel in the day.

00:09:31.232 --> 00:09:39.378
So, they were trying to get through in the nighttime and they were using the stars as a map so they wouldn't get lost.

00:09:39.627 --> 00:09:43.106
And that's what I was seeing in the spirit.

00:09:59.573 --> 00:10:00.040
But they were looking for the North Star.

00:10:08.080 --> 00:10:08.423
And I thought that was really interesting because that's how detailed these visions were last night.

00:10:15.680 --> 00:10:25.880
I could see them, and they had little bitty fire torches, and they were trying to move through areas, and I was like, "What in the world, Lord?

00:10:36.457 --> 00:10:41.222
" And as I'm looking and able to look over there, I see them praying and singing old songs.

00:10:49.960 --> 00:10:50.570
And there were old—not Pentecostal songs, but old Bible songs like hymnals, old hymns, old songs that we don't sing anymore.

00:10:53.146 --> 00:11:04.968
I was trying to listen because I was hearing, and this is what's amazing: I've never been in a vision and heard people singing before.

00:11:10.726 --> 00:11:15.039
I could hear the African-American people singing, the women and the men, and it was a deep, heavy song.

00:11:23.432 --> 00:11:23.680
It wasn't joyful.

00:11:24.187 --> 00:11:25.200
It was heavy, like groanings in the spirit.

00:11:25.200 --> 00:11:26.720
It was heavy, asking the Father for freedom.

00:11:26.720 --> 00:11:27.1000
"Where are you?

00:11:27.1000 --> 00:11:30.102
Why have you forgotten us?

00:11:30.102 --> 00:11:32.640
Why are we going through this?

00:11:32.640 --> 00:11:37.360
" crying out for the Father to redeem them and set them free.

00:11:46.880 --> 00:11:47.140
And as I saw them praying, I saw a man named Abraham Lincoln.

00:11:47.140 --> 00:11:52.213
And God raised up a man named Abraham Lincoln to do what he did to bring freedom to the slaves.

00:11:52.213 --> 00:11:53.505
And I saw them murder him.

00:11:53.505 --> 00:12:09.840
I saw all this stuff panned out, and he was a really tall man, and some people say, "Well, he was 6'4"," but with his top hat—I saw his hat, and it made him look like he was a lot bigger.

00:12:09.840 --> 00:12:15.591
I'm telling you in the vision—and this is another thing—was everybody else a lot smaller?

00:12:15.591 --> 00:12:26.376
Because he looked like he was head and shoulders above everybody, from these men that were below him.

00:12:26.376 --> 00:12:31.804
So I'm like, well, maybe people weren't very tall back then.

00:12:31.804 --> 00:12:44.959
I don't know, because when I saw him, he was like a really big guy in this black suit in the vision, and I'm still trying to figure out what I saw.

00:12:44.959 --> 00:12:48.274
I'm like, was he standing next to kids?

00:13:00.639 --> 00:13:00.879
I don't know.

00:13:00.879 --> 00:13:10.320
All I know is I tell you these things, but I saw he was a lot bigger of a man than everybody else was.

00:13:10.320 --> 00:13:17.560
So maybe everybody else is like 5'5" or something.

00:13:21.528 --> 00:13:24.640
I don't know.

00:13:24.640 --> 00:13:29.614
They didn't look like they were very big people.

00:13:29.614 --> 00:13:31.394
Does it matter?

00:13:31.394 --> 00:13:32.128
No.

00:13:32.128 --> 00:13:34.440
I just try to figure it out.

00:13:34.440 --> 00:13:40.937
I love when the Lord shows me things, and I take it very seriously.

00:13:40.937 --> 00:13:42.782
It's His love language towards me.

00:13:42.782 --> 00:13:43.369
It's intimacy.

00:13:43.369 --> 00:13:46.880
It's how I learn how to communicate with Him.

00:13:52.560 --> 00:13:52.879
And He shows me things.

00:13:58.879 --> 00:14:03.840
And it's something that I never thought I would ever go public about to the point like I am now, that 70,000 people would look at it a day.

00:14:03.840 --> 00:14:11.448
But I know a lot of you are just desperate and want intimacy with Him.

00:14:11.448 --> 00:14:13.120
That's why you're here.

00:14:22.782 --> 00:14:23.146
You want your own relationship.

00:14:23.146 --> 00:14:27.383
And the Lord wants you to have it.

00:14:27.383 --> 00:14:33.880
He's no respecter of persons, but He is a respecter of those that seek Him.

00:14:33.880 --> 00:14:41.200
And I want to tell you, as you seek Him, you'll find Him.

00:14:41.200 --> 00:14:51.800
But when He told me He was going to bring a restitution—restitution, but with interest.

00:14:51.800 --> 00:14:53.760
With interest.

00:15:06.515 --> 00:15:06.737
And people say, 'Well, how's that going to happen?

00:15:06.737 --> 00:15:08.079
' I don't know.

00:15:16.859 --> 00:15:17.469
It's in the spirit.

00:15:31.506 --> 00:15:31.839
And if God said He would reward those and bring that to them, you can take it to the bank.

00:15:31.839 --> 00:15:33.640
My Father is able.

00:15:33.640 --> 00:15:46.800
I'm not going to question the God of the universe, the God of everything, and go, 'Well, how are you going to do that with my peanut brain?

00:15:46.800 --> 00:15:57.499
' when He can make manna out of nothing, turn the water into wine, do all the things that He's always done, and do super exceedingly abundantly above all that you dare ask or think.

00:15:57.499 --> 00:16:02.592
If He said He would do it, He's able, and I don't question it.

00:16:17.360 --> 00:16:17.670
I just go, He told me to tell you for you to believe for it.

00:16:23.109 --> 00:16:33.965
And those of you that are in the young generation, if those others have gone home—your elders have gone home, because I saw 80 years old, 90 years old, and I didn't know why I was seeing that.

00:16:33.965 --> 00:16:41.330
But if you were a child in the 1921 race riots, you'd still be here probably, right?

00:16:41.330 --> 00:16:43.729
That's only 104 years ago.

00:16:43.729 --> 00:16:44.629
Yeah.

00:16:44.629 --> 00:16:48.720
So if you were a child, you're still here probably, right?

00:16:48.720 --> 00:16:52.880
No, well, no, to be born, they'd probably be dead.

00:16:52.880 --> 00:16:54.320
Yeah, if possible.

00:16:54.320 --> 00:16:56.299
I mean, they're like 106, 107.

00:16:57.659 --> 00:16:57.889
It's very, very unlikely.

00:16:57.889 --> 00:16:58.580
Pretty rare.

00:16:58.580 --> 00:16:59.417
Very unlikely.

00:17:05.965 --> 00:17:06.530
So, it's their grandchildren.

00:17:06.530 --> 00:17:07.660
Yeah.

00:17:11.580 --> 00:17:14.490
It would be their grandchild or their children.

00:17:14.490 --> 00:17:21.353
Their children would probably still be here.

00:17:21.353 --> 00:17:24.739
They were raised still up underneath that.

00:17:24.739 --> 00:17:27.059
They're old, though.

00:17:42.444 --> 00:17:42.712
That would be the 80 and 90 years old probably that I was seeing in the spirit realm.

00:17:54.013 --> 00:17:54.707
The Lord was showing me that He was still bringing restitution for them.

00:17:54.707 --> 00:17:56.093
Right.

00:18:07.715 --> 00:18:08.090
So, wow.

00:18:08.090 --> 00:18:10.700
It's just time goes.

00:18:10.700 --> 00:18:26.353
But after I see what the Lord is showing me, for you to believe just like it was for Diana to believe for her ancestors—ancestors, they didn't get the restitution.

00:18:26.353 --> 00:18:32.604
You know, they get Indian land, tribal benefits, and things like that.

00:18:34.427 --> 00:18:39.340
And but the Lord was showing me making the wrong right, making the wrong right, that He had not forgotten it.

00:18:40.740 --> 00:18:41.880
And it's not brushed underneath the rug.

00:18:50.160 --> 00:18:50.503
It's time to take the rug off.

00:18:59.092 --> 00:18:59.506
And the white folks, I realize there's a lot more ignorant people than what you think.

00:18:59.506 --> 00:19:05.591
It's like Diana, and I told her we got some dumb emails, but you know what, people are...

00:19:05.591 --> 00:19:06.773
it's the devil behind them.

00:19:06.773 --> 00:19:07.947
They don't understand.

00:19:07.947 --> 00:19:15.926
They're blinded by their own religious Pharisee, racist, bigoted ways.

00:19:24.080 --> 00:19:24.440
And that's what it is.

00:19:26.727 --> 00:19:34.120
I use these hard words, but my goodness, folks, we have some really ignorant people.

00:19:40.800 --> 00:19:42.560
And you go, 'Okay, I'm not inciting any kind of violence.

00:19:42.560 --> 00:19:46.422
I'm not inciting people to get upset.

00:19:46.422 --> 00:19:52.308
' I'm trying to tell you the Father wants to restore you.

00:20:04.427 --> 00:20:04.649
The Father wants to restore you.

00:20:14.080 --> 00:20:14.420
And that's all it's about with me.

00:20:23.760 --> 00:20:24.040
I'm obedient unto Him unto death.

00:20:26.446 --> 00:20:26.697
And when He says speak, I speak.

00:20:31.143 --> 00:20:39.880
And this is what the Spirit of the Lord wanted to say to you yesterday: that He loves you, and He's not forgotten you.

00:20:48.320 --> 00:20:51.200
And the pain of the past, He's going to give you back more than what you ever...

00:20:51.200 --> 00:20:53.571
it's more than sevenfold.

00:20:53.571 --> 00:21:00.360
He said, 'I'm going to restore back all the money.

00:21:00.360 --> 00:21:06.836
' So 400 years of wealth, if you'll believe for it.

00:21:06.836 --> 00:21:10.039
400 years of family bloodline back pay with interest.

00:21:10.524 --> 00:21:15.954
And I was like, that's millions of dollars in my opinion.

00:21:21.760 --> 00:21:25.840
I mean, so believe God for big.

00:21:25.840 --> 00:21:27.880
Believe God for big.

00:21:27.880 --> 00:21:29.039
Why not?

00:21:29.039 --> 00:21:41.387
If He said He would do it, believe for it.

00:21:46.760 --> 00:21:47.240
And so that was what I had for you today of that, just rehearsing things.

00:21:47.240 --> 00:21:59.840
Now, side note, that was precious in itself, but the things I'm seeing about Israel and the baby wrapped in the blanket with Israel, I don't understand all that.

00:21:59.840 --> 00:22:03.817
A rebirthing, new things are going to take place.

00:22:03.817 --> 00:22:06.137
So, what a patriotism.

00:22:06.137 --> 00:22:13.501
There's something about patriotism from June, this next month today, going all the way into July—of patriotism.

00:22:13.501 --> 00:22:17.580
There's something, and people say, 'You say what's going to happen in 24 hours.

00:22:17.580 --> 00:22:22.480
' Everything will change within a 24-hour period whenever you'll see it.

00:22:32.143 --> 00:22:32.879
I don't know.

00:22:32.879 --> 00:22:34.913
That's just...

00:22:42.251 --> 00:22:42.702
I just hear this, and I am like an antenna.

00:22:53.840 --> 00:22:55.740
I have my little antenna up and you're picking up from the receiver.

00:23:03.890 --> 00:23:06.110
I have my receiver, and I have the main broadcast going on, and my little antenna is going beep-beep like my little radio, and I'm picking up my radio, my Bible.

00:23:06.110 --> 00:23:14.888
And I got this, and it's downloaded into me that God says that everything you know is going to change within a 24-hour period.

00:23:14.888 --> 00:23:23.503
And I hear that and I go, I'm relaying it back as, 'This is what the Spirit of the Lord tells me to tell you.

00:23:23.503 --> 00:23:29.486
' And everything's going to change within a 24-hour period.

00:23:29.486 --> 00:23:32.400
Everything you know—a great shaking to awaken is coming.

00:23:32.400 --> 00:23:34.017
A great shaking to awaken is coming.

00:23:34.222 --> 00:23:40.600
I saw a great war breaking out with Israel and Iran in the days ahead.

00:23:50.039 --> 00:23:55.573
And I told you back in January that I saw an American missile striking a mountain that was an underground city, and Iran set all kinds of deterrents trying to stop this missile.

00:24:00.800 --> 00:24:01.120
It was a very powerful one.

00:24:13.039 --> 00:24:13.279
But when Israel does this, I saw that they set Iran back financially, globally, nuclearly, everything.

00:24:13.279 --> 00:24:15.645
They put them back in the Stone Age.

00:24:22.719 --> 00:24:22.986
I heard the Spirit of the Lord say, 'They put them back in the Stone Age.

00:24:22.986 --> 00:24:30.286
' But when they do this, they strike their oil and their gasoline plants, their petroleum plants, right?

00:24:32.440 --> 00:24:33.360
I saw like gas, I saw, you know, these refineries.

00:24:33.360 --> 00:24:34.693
Thank you, Holy Spirit.

00:24:34.693 --> 00:24:39.733
I'm trying, y'all, because, I'm telling you, these names and these big names, I don't use them.

00:24:39.733 --> 00:24:40.124
Refineries.

00:24:40.836 --> 00:24:41.093
I saw refineries.

00:24:46.704 --> 00:24:46.880
And when they strike the refineries, I saw gas and oil prices skyrocketing.

00:25:02.846 --> 00:25:03.223
I've warned you of this since 2023, about this for a season, for a season.

00:25:05.760 --> 00:25:07.580
And then the Lord showed me in that vision the 1970 gas wars.

00:25:08.880 --> 00:25:12.186
I saw cars lined up down the blocks because of gas shortages.

00:25:20.089 --> 00:25:20.507
Now, if that still happens, I don't know, but this is what I saw.

00:25:20.507 --> 00:25:22.272
This is in 2023.

00:25:23.552 --> 00:25:31.359
And the Lord told me at this time that gas would skyrocket, and it would bring the price of oil up really high, really high.

00:25:37.130 --> 00:25:38.960
I saw it going up to $200 a barrel, like big money trying to flow, which would stimulate the American economy.

00:25:49.183 --> 00:25:51.549
It stimulated the American economy whenever these big oil productions get hit in the Middle East.

00:25:56.160 --> 00:25:58.615
And it would happen for a season, for a window.

00:26:01.770 --> 00:26:02.020
I don't know how long, for a window.

00:26:06.536 --> 00:26:07.039
And I saw gas in the Mediterranean being drilled.

00:26:13.733 --> 00:26:14.097
I saw the Gulf of—people want to argue America—Gulf of Mexico.

00:26:14.097 --> 00:26:15.555
I don't care.

00:26:15.555 --> 00:26:17.052
Call it what you want.

00:26:17.052 --> 00:26:18.300
They were drilling, drilling, drilling, drilling.

00:26:20.869 --> 00:26:21.314
And I saw, "drill, baby, drill.

00:26:31.039 --> 00:26:31.279
" I saw pipelines being opened up, being worked out, making big agreements for pipelines.

00:26:47.409 --> 00:26:47.784
The Nord Stream pipeline, I believe, is what it's called.

00:26:57.813 --> 00:26:58.186
It was the big pipeline.

00:26:58.186 --> 00:27:07.650
I saw it being talked about and opened up, working on it, just trying to get this pipe deal going, doing major oil big deals ahead, stimulating America's economy.

00:27:07.650 --> 00:27:16.640
But when this happens, I saw great antisemitism because of people being mad at Israel about what they're about to do.

00:27:16.640 --> 00:27:17.493
Remember this.

00:27:17.493 --> 00:27:21.300
I saw them wanting to retaliate with war: Russia, Syria, Turkey.

00:27:32.960 --> 00:27:33.400
I saw them getting upset, and the Middle East, against, "Well, you did all that.

00:27:33.400 --> 00:27:36.080
We're going to come after you.

00:27:36.080 --> 00:27:40.960
" So, will we see all this in the days ahead?

00:27:49.680 --> 00:27:49.920
I don't know, folks.

00:27:58.950 --> 00:27:59.160
All I know is these are visions that I've seen.

00:28:06.343 --> 00:28:06.651
Have we changed it through prayer?

00:28:06.651 --> 00:28:08.014
I don't believe we have.

00:28:09.068 --> 00:28:10.039
We hear some of this on the news now.

00:28:10.039 --> 00:28:14.296
Some of the things that I see take years to come to pass.

00:28:14.296 --> 00:28:17.800
Sometimes it takes 10 years, you know, I don't know.

00:28:17.800 --> 00:28:18.800
Sometimes it's months.

00:28:28.891 --> 00:28:29.257
So, let's pray for President Trump.

00:28:29.257 --> 00:28:33.080
Remember I told you I kept hearing him say, "I want to go about this...

00:28:33.080 --> 00:28:37.973
" I told you in January, I said he said, "I want to go about this diplomatically.

00:28:37.973 --> 00:28:39.930
I'm not pushing the button.

00:28:39.930 --> 00:28:43.849
I'm not pushing the button, but Israel did it anyway.

00:28:43.849 --> 00:28:44.452
" Remember?

00:28:44.452 --> 00:28:50.286
But then I've been praying and I've told you all I see a black swan event.

00:28:56.019 --> 00:28:56.189
We got to create a boogeyman.

00:29:00.596 --> 00:29:00.773
I hear him say we have to create an enemy so that it justifies our reaction.

00:29:00.773 --> 00:29:02.293
We're going to have to retaliate and make...

00:29:02.293 --> 00:29:03.200
We have a ripe cause.

00:29:08.587 --> 00:29:08.960
Like, you know they're bad.

00:29:08.960 --> 00:29:11.950
We have to stop these bad people, right?

00:29:11.950 --> 00:29:16.456
But all of it was about nuclear power, about oil, about a lot of things.

00:29:16.456 --> 00:29:21.320
So, just what I've seen, you take it for what it's worth.

00:29:43.135 --> 00:29:43.510
I mean, it's a lot to us, right?

00:29:43.510 --> 00:29:44.260
Yes.

00:29:49.780 --> 00:29:56.835
And we pray over it and I take everything the Lord shows me to prayer every single time, and I intercede over it, and this is my job.

00:29:56.835 --> 00:29:59.893
You're just a part of it now.

00:29:59.893 --> 00:30:02.413
It's very public, but it's what we do.

00:30:02.413 --> 00:30:05.714
I've been doing it, like I said, for a long time.

00:30:11.927 --> 00:30:12.217
My whole marriage.

00:30:12.217 --> 00:30:13.576
Yes, for sure.

00:30:19.040 --> 00:30:20.000
This is what we do, and we take notes and we write down what the Lord tells us.

00:30:26.799 --> 00:30:27.075
And that's why it's become so big.

00:30:29.589 --> 00:30:29.899
It wasn't like this at first.

00:30:30.209 --> 00:30:32.950
It's taken development, and he would show me glimpses of things.

00:30:34.697 --> 00:30:36.297
And as I've been faithful with little, he gives me more and more and more.

00:30:40.320 --> 00:30:47.139
And now it's really cool because whenever I get close to...

00:30:47.139 --> 00:30:54.382
Like, if we're believing for something and Diana says, "I need you to pray for me.

00:31:07.140 --> 00:31:07.560
I'm overcoming a headache or something," you know, I don't know, I just give her an instance.

00:31:13.680 --> 00:31:18.979
I can touch her now, or she can, or I can my kids, and the Lord will show me exactly what's going on and how to fix it, what to pray, everything.

00:31:20.240 --> 00:31:20.651
And that's part of the healing part.

00:31:26.648 --> 00:31:26.897
And it's developing and developing and developing.

00:31:28.142 --> 00:31:28.391
And it's very interesting.

00:31:32.453 --> 00:31:32.680
But I just told you something I don't ever talk about, but it's very interesting.

00:31:32.680 --> 00:31:33.133
Amazing.

00:31:34.366 --> 00:31:37.851
The root cause, everything, where it stems from, how it got there, things like that, with people.

00:31:37.851 --> 00:31:42.453
And it's all glory to God, folks, because I am nothing without him.

00:31:42.453 --> 00:31:46.480
It's all about Jesus and what he's done, and he gives us gifts to walk in.

00:31:46.480 --> 00:31:47.200
I'm nothing special.

00:31:47.200 --> 00:31:48.023
I'm just Brandon.

00:31:48.023 --> 00:31:52.891
I'm just grateful that everybody would want to show up every single day and want to pray with me.

00:31:52.891 --> 00:31:56.039
Thank you.

00:32:10.480 --> 00:32:10.711
And there are some people so kind.

00:32:10.711 --> 00:32:18.169
It's like one dear sister, "Hey, if everybody gives them a dollar, if everybody gives them a dollar, you can stop eBay and Poshmark.

00:32:25.1000 --> 00:32:28.349
" And I told Diana, I said, "Our people are kind, such good hearts.

00:32:48.025 --> 00:32:48.410
" We thought about doing a book thing.

00:32:48.410 --> 00:32:54.352
Diana and I pray about doing books; we pray about doing all these things.

00:32:54.352 --> 00:33:10.000
But she said, even in the car, she said, "Brandon, even if I did a book deal, I could write a book, Brandon, but we are such givers that even if we did it, most people...

00:33:10.000 --> 00:33:21.616
You see these big ministries, everybody writes a book about every year, and they sell them for $25 a piece.

00:33:22.320 --> 00:33:27.279
And if they sell 100,000 copies of those, that's a lot of money.

00:33:27.279 --> 00:33:30.399
You know, they're making millions.

00:33:35.916 --> 00:33:37.020
" And so our heart is, immediately, we just want to give everything away.

00:33:38.619 --> 00:33:49.559
And so she's like, "Even if I wrote the book, we would put all our finances into making a book and we would give it all away, Brandon," she goes, "because it would be hard.

00:33:49.559 --> 00:33:58.533
It would bother me to sell a book for 25 bucks, unless the Lord told us to do it to fund our ministry.

00:34:13.470 --> 00:34:13.855
" But my heart is to give, because freely I have received, freely I give.

00:34:13.855 --> 00:34:14.800
I just...

00:34:14.800 --> 00:34:15.920
Books, tapes, CDs.

00:34:18.639 --> 00:34:26.587
I would wait for days, weeks, save up my money to be able to buy a tape series whenever a special guest speaker came to church.

00:34:26.587 --> 00:34:32.463
And I would go, "Oh, Diana, can we use our tithes to buy those this month?

00:34:32.463 --> 00:34:37.320
" Because that was our treat.

00:34:37.320 --> 00:34:39.234
That was our treat.

00:34:39.234 --> 00:34:46.857
And Diana goes, "Just think of if they were all free, how much further along we'd be.

00:34:46.857 --> 00:34:50.296
" Because we had to wait for weeks to get it.

00:34:50.296 --> 00:35:03.160
And when the next guest speaker came, we didn't have money to buy it, so we had to wait.

00:35:18.720 --> 00:35:20.280
And so we were always trying to put money back to buy these tape series or CD series or MP4s or whatever.

00:35:20.280 --> 00:35:23.115
And it was always like, oh.

00:35:23.115 --> 00:35:26.800
She goes, "Which one can we have today?

00:35:52.740 --> 00:35:53.320
" And I'm like, "Well, we get one.

00:35:53.320 --> 00:35:56.463
We can have one.

00:35:56.463 --> 00:35:59.200
It's $35.

00:36:05.647 --> 00:36:05.973
" And she goes, "Oh, okay.

00:36:16.937 --> 00:36:17.343
I see five I really want.

00:36:17.343 --> 00:36:19.688
" That's the way we work.

00:36:19.688 --> 00:36:22.288
We're always so hungry.

00:36:22.288 --> 00:36:36.430
Thank God for YouTube now because we can find a lot of those on there.

00:36:37.190 --> 00:36:39.440
We just push the button, it's there.

00:36:39.440 --> 00:36:52.239
But back in the early 2000s and when we were kids, it was all like $5 a cassette tape, you know, five bucks.

00:36:52.239 --> 00:36:59.480
And then when it was $5 a cassette tape times...

00:37:11.422 --> 00:37:11.786
It was a four-cassette tape series.

00:37:11.786 --> 00:37:18.270
If the series went on long, the more, the bigger, the more tapes there were, it'd be up to 100 bucks.

00:37:23.055 --> 00:37:24.496
And we were like, "Oh my God, it's so much money.

00:37:44.335 --> 00:37:44.800
" And we were so excited to get it if we put our money back.

00:37:51.284 --> 00:37:51.599
So I always tell her, I said, "Can we take our tithe and do it?

00:37:55.217 --> 00:37:55.554
" You know, because I'm so hungry.

00:37:55.554 --> 00:38:00.416
But even doing stuff like that now, I go, "Diana, could you even imagine?

00:38:00.912 --> 00:38:02.152
" I mean, because I feel guilty.

00:38:21.451 --> 00:38:21.789
I wouldn't be able to do it.

00:38:27.200 --> 00:38:27.980
I just give it all away.

00:38:29.182 --> 00:38:30.449
I remember those days.

00:38:52.663 --> 00:38:53.269
To give a book away, you know, hungry.

00:38:53.269 --> 00:38:56.729
Golly, I'm crying too much today.

00:38:58.599 --> 00:38:58.859
I got to cry again.

00:38:58.859 --> 00:39:08.760
Most people went to movies, but we just saved all our money to buy tapes and books.

00:39:08.760 --> 00:39:11.885
It's the way it's always been, though.

00:39:11.885 --> 00:39:24.377
You just want change so bad in your life, and you know that the word would change you if you can get it in you.

00:39:34.420 --> 00:39:34.850
And there are so many ministers that charge for that stuff, and I'm not condemning it.

00:39:34.850 --> 00:39:39.520
I know it costs money to get it out.

00:39:39.520 --> 00:39:40.799
I get it.

00:39:47.555 --> 00:39:47.870
But in my heart, you'd go bankrupt because I'd give everything I have, these books, all this stuff.

00:39:47.870 --> 00:39:53.119
And I see all these big ministers make books all the time.

00:39:53.119 --> 00:39:55.970
They've got brand new books.

00:39:55.970 --> 00:40:02.440
"I've got a brand new book, $35, 25 bucks.

00:40:26.436 --> 00:40:26.631
" And I'm like, "Oh, yeah, and now I could buy it.

00:40:26.631 --> 00:40:27.804
" But it's not the point.

00:40:27.804 --> 00:40:31.149
There's a lot of you that couldn't.

00:40:34.524 --> 00:40:34.907
And I remember the day that I couldn't.

00:40:37.583 --> 00:40:40.600
And that's why it's like, "Do you want to write a book?

00:40:40.600 --> 00:40:43.880
" People ask me, "Brandon, write a book.

00:40:43.880 --> 00:40:47.580
" People come to me all the time: "Write a book.

00:40:55.748 --> 00:40:56.079
" And I'm like, even if I did, a book deal wouldn't do you any good.

00:40:56.079 --> 00:41:00.200
It bothers me to want to charge for it.

00:41:00.200 --> 00:41:02.546
Maybe I shouldn't be that way.

00:41:02.546 --> 00:41:16.144
Maybe it should be that I charge for it for the ministry and grow it that way, and, say you sell 100,000 books at $25 a piece, you fund your ministry, and maybe that's how it works.

00:41:16.144 --> 00:41:17.453
I don't know.

00:41:17.453 --> 00:41:20.555
I'm new to all this, y'all.

00:41:20.555 --> 00:41:23.973
I'm new to all of it.

00:41:23.973 --> 00:41:29.213
But I'm hungry and I want more, and I seek the Lord.

00:41:29.213 --> 00:41:46.119
But then there are people who say, "You know, we had that t-shirt thing on there," and I thought, "Well, everybody likes a t-shirt for 25 bucks, you know?

00:41:46.119 --> 00:41:50.800
They want to support us, you know, whatever.

00:42:06.225 --> 00:42:06.570
" And I had it on there, and I took it down because they were too slow and I didn't have anybody to make good t-shirts.

00:42:06.570 --> 00:42:10.400
But I thought, "Well, everybody has to wear clothes.

00:42:10.400 --> 00:42:21.648
Clothes are not free, but if they put a design on them, they want to wear a t-shirt to church, you know?

00:42:21.648 --> 00:42:24.880
" So, I thought that's kind of neat.

00:42:24.880 --> 00:42:41.710
But then the company said, "You should be charging this," but I charged a lot less than what it was because I wanted people to have it for a good deal.

00:42:51.340 --> 00:42:51.784
And I told them, I said, "I feel bad charging high-dollar prices, four times what it's worth.

00:43:04.605 --> 00:43:05.016
You know, people work hard for what they have.

00:43:05.016 --> 00:43:24.800
" When you make what I made being a janitor for so long—you clean all that nasty stuff, all those toilets, and you do that for so long, and clean out the brownie bags, clean out the feminine cans, and do all the things that I did by the thousands—you just respect people more.

00:43:32.408 --> 00:43:32.550
And I don't cry about this.

00:43:32.550 --> 00:43:33.897
There's just a lot I'm dealing with.

00:43:33.897 --> 00:43:39.954
But it is just interesting because of what the Lord is just talking to me.

00:43:39.954 --> 00:43:42.320
He's just dealing with me a lot.

00:43:48.980 --> 00:43:49.400
So, I appreciate all of you.

00:44:18.130 --> 00:44:18.575
I appreciate you coming.

00:44:31.020 --> 00:44:31.240
I appreciate Diana.

00:44:31.240 --> 00:44:44.524
We love this prayer time with you, that we could just teach even just one of you how to touch the hem of His garment with what we've done, and that the intimacy of our relationship would become real to you.

00:44:44.524 --> 00:44:46.231
Maybe it would inspire you.

00:44:46.231 --> 00:44:52.180
You know, this is my book, so that you could be inspired.

00:44:53.775 --> 00:45:02.680
I think I was just so touched that the Father would want me to pray for the African-American people the way He did last night and have it be on me so heavy today with the anointing.

00:45:05.560 --> 00:45:05.749
What an honor!

00:45:07.279 --> 00:45:16.680
I thought, "What an honor to touch a great group of people and be able to be a part of their journey, and just pray for them like I did.

00:45:16.680 --> 00:45:34.220
" I got to just for that 24 hours, and it's like today it was still so heavy on me, and I thought, "Who am I, Lord, that the God of the universe, the 'I AM THAT I AM,' would come and visit me and say, 'Hey, I have an assignment for you.

00:45:34.220 --> 00:45:35.430
You live in Tulsa.

00:45:35.430 --> 00:45:35.850
'?

00:45:35.850 --> 00:45:37.920
" He could have used anybody.

00:45:37.920 --> 00:45:41.828
There are so many amazing ministers around here.

00:46:00.866 --> 00:46:01.407
He could have used anybody, but I do this in my little room in my house with a green screen, and I just come on here and tell you about Jesus.

00:46:01.407 --> 00:46:05.766
So, let's pray today.

00:46:05.766 --> 00:46:20.870
I pray this video blessed you and what we said.

00:46:20.880 --> 00:46:43.660
I just thought it was cool just to talk about some things and just be more real, you know.

00:46:43.660 --> 00:46:47.680
So, all right.

00:46:47.680 --> 00:46:51.722
Well, let's pray today.

00:46:51.722 --> 00:46:56.599
All right.

00:46:56.599 --> 00:47:14.667
Let's see if the Lord shows us anything else new today.

00:47:14.667 --> 00:47:20.487
It's His time.

00:47:20.487 --> 00:47:23.992
All right.

00:47:23.992 --> 00:47:30.839
I'm going to take communion.

00:47:30.839 --> 00:47:39.415
I'll take it with you.

00:48:49.689 --> 00:48:50.138
I don't want this to become, you know, whenever you desensitize it when you do something so robotically that it loses meaning.

00:48:50.138 --> 00:48:53.280
That's why I skipped it yesterday.

00:49:11.423 --> 00:50:16.872
The Lord said to me, He goes, "Don't let this become robotic, taking a wafer, taking the juice, and not going deep inside your heart of what it truly means.

00:50:16.872 --> 00:50:22.319
Don't let it become a religious ritual.

00:50:39.360 --> 00:50:40.219
" A ritual.

00:51:16.770 --> 00:51:18.390
Thank you.

00:51:18.390 --> 00:51:35.079
A ritual that you do that is just like putting on your shoes or your clothes, right?

00:51:54.093 --> 00:51:55.187
This is holy.

00:52:56.497 --> 00:52:58.155
This is holy.

00:52:58.155 --> 00:53:07.077
This deserves great respect.

00:53:07.077 --> 00:53:25.081
This is something that cost somebody everything—our Lord and Savior.

00:53:25.081 --> 00:53:34.030
Do you understand?

00:54:33.426 --> 00:54:34.599
This cost Him everything.

00:54:34.599 --> 00:54:51.223
He paid the price for everything, and this is what it represents.

00:55:00.824 --> 00:55:10.249
This isn't something that you do like putting on your clothes or taking a bath.

00:55:17.010 --> 00:55:22.839
This is holy.

00:55:53.640 --> 00:55:57.366
And whenever the Holy Spirit tells me, He says, "Brandon, you're not being respectful enough with it in your heart.

00:55:57.366 --> 00:56:01.730
Be reverent.

00:56:01.730 --> 00:56:05.079
Reverence.

00:56:05.079 --> 00:56:07.120
Pause.

00:56:07.120 --> 00:56:10.600
It's holy.

00:56:10.600 --> 00:56:13.840
It's holy.

00:56:13.840 --> 00:56:16.540
It's holy.

00:56:16.540 --> 00:56:30.599
" So, we go to Him with holy communion.

00:56:30.599 --> 00:56:54.400
We go to Him because His blood is enough for you and me.

00:56:54.400 --> 00:57:14.040
We go to Him because He is worthy of our praise.

00:57:14.040 --> 00:57:33.647
He is—this is beautiful.

00:58:11.343 --> 00:58:13.047
This is relationship.

00:58:25.040 --> 00:58:26.760
This is not religion.

00:58:26.760 --> 00:58:36.212
This is not Catholic.

00:58:36.212 --> 00:58:42.160
This is not Protestant.

00:58:42.160 --> 00:59:06.960
This is relationship.

00:59:06.960 --> 00:59:07.760
Do you understand?

00:59:07.760 --> 01:00:05.760
To me, it is.

01:00:20.320 --> 01:00:30.799
It may be something else to you because of the way you were raised, but this is something that has become so holy to me, precious.

01:00:30.799 --> 01:00:35.234
This is my key and my ticket.

01:00:35.234 --> 01:00:37.386
I sit at His feet.

01:01:03.407 --> 01:01:03.760
You want to know a relationship?

01:01:03.760 --> 01:01:05.440
This is what based it: communion.

01:01:05.440 --> 01:01:14.423
It's why I'm so big on it, because it was something that came out of hard times.

01:01:30.345 --> 01:01:43.556
This came out of hell, going through it, going to Him and saying, "Father, I need You.

01:01:53.144 --> 01:01:53.689
I need more of You.

01:01:53.689 --> 01:02:02.040
" And that's why I look at it probably so much more differently than everybody else.

01:02:02.040 --> 01:02:11.120
And there are a lot of you that get very mad at me.

01:02:11.120 --> 01:02:13.520
"You just honor it.

01:02:13.520 --> 01:02:18.750
You do this.

01:02:18.760 --> 01:02:21.091
" No, no, no.

01:02:40.000 --> 01:02:40.320
I honor it with my whole heart.

01:02:40.320 --> 01:02:45.179
This means more to me than anything you can ever imagine.

01:02:45.179 --> 01:02:50.990
This means more to me than some priest giving it to me.

01:02:50.990 --> 01:02:58.599
This means to me something so much more than what you can ever comprehend.

01:02:58.599 --> 01:03:12.519
So, Father, I lift it up before You today, and I thank You.

01:03:16.966 --> 01:03:39.544
I thank You for Your body that was broken for us, something so holy and so innocent for me.

01:03:41.860 --> 01:04:21.748
I come before Your feet, not as an adult, but as a child with childlike faith.

01:04:21.748 --> 01:04:22.852
"Father, I'm broken.

01:04:22.852 --> 01:04:50.296
I need You to fix it.

01:04:50.296 --> 01:06:40.520
" All the pains, all the hurts, all the things that I go through on a day-to-day basis, Father, You make me whole.

01:06:40.520 --> 01:06:54.792
You put the pieces back together again.

01:07:17.754 --> 01:07:21.447
And all these people that are hurting from race riots, all the things in the past from all these deep roots of pain throughout the whole world—there's been like, I was criticized so much.

01:07:21.447 --> 01:07:24.400
"There's so many more people than that, Brandon.

01:07:24.400 --> 01:07:42.577
" But those are the ones the Lord had on His heart yesterday, from the Jews that got in the camps with Hitler and all the stuff with the Holocaust.

01:07:42.577 --> 01:07:46.684
So much pain from so many people.

01:07:46.684 --> 01:07:56.267
We know that a lot of people have went through a lot of things over the course of history.

01:08:07.039 --> 01:08:07.719
But so we just lift up every single ethnic group all around the world.

01:08:07.719 --> 01:08:17.324
No matter what you've been through, Jesus knows all the pain you go through.

01:08:17.324 --> 01:08:22.355
Every tribe, every tongue, doesn't matter how far it lies.

01:08:22.355 --> 01:08:30.551
Jesus paid the price for you to walk in freedom from that pain.

01:08:30.551 --> 01:08:34.611
Jew, Gentile, all of us.

01:08:34.611 --> 01:08:39.400
Thank you, Father.

